Package ca.klapstein.baudit.Activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountCreateActivity
    Activity presenting a account creation page for Baudit.
    AddProblemActivity
    Activity for adding a Problem to a Patient.
    AddRecordActivity
    Activity for adding a Record to a Problem.
    BodyLocationDialog
    Dialog providing a prompt to pick a location on a BodyPhoto thus obtaining a set of BodyPhotoCoords
    CreateCareProviderAccountActivity
    Activity providing the inputs and validations for creating a valid CareProvider Account for Baudit.
    CreatePatientAccountActivity
    Activity providing the inputs and validations for creating a valid Patient Account for Baudit.
    DeleteDialog
    Abstract class defining the basis for DeleteProblemDialog and DeleteRecordDialog.
    DeleteProblemDialog
    Dialog providing a confirmation prompt to delete a Problem.
    DeleteRecordDialog
    Dialog providing a confirmation prompt to delete a Record.
    EditAccountActivity
    Activity for editing a User.
    EditProblemActivity
    Activity for editing a Problem.
    EditRecordActivity
    Activity for editing a Record.
    LocationActivity
    Activity for displaying and choosing a location on a map.
    LoginActivity
    Activity presenting a login page for Baudit.
    LogoutDialog
    Dialog providing a logout prompt.
    MainActivity
    Starting Activity for Baudit.
    PatientListActivity
    Activity for listing Patients.
    PhotoActivity
    Activity providing a camera widget to take photos for use in Baudit.
    ProblemActivity
    Abstract Class for interacting with a instance of a Problem.
    ProblemListActivity
    Activity for listing Problems.
    RecordActivity
    Abstract Class for interacting with a instance of a Record.
    RecordListActivity
    Activity for listing Records.
    SlideShowDialog
    Dialog providing a "slideshow" of photos to be easily viewed.
    ViewAccountDialog
    Dialog providing a overview of an User.
